  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>An open-world sand-box game where you play as a cat, defying the rules and causing mayhem. Climb, scratch, and pounce your way through the cityscape filled with playful challenges and hidden secrets. Customise your cat, team up with friends and let the adventure begin!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Cat Chaos</h2>Take your chaos to new heights as you collaborate on the city streets. Hijack cars, cause explosive distractions, and equip a variety of weapons to create the ultimate cat caper. Show off your agile moves with purr-fect parkour skills. Leap from rooftop to rooftop, scale walls, and pull off gravity-defying stunts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Side</h2>Enter Kitty City, where Chief Hairris’ Purrlice force engages in an ongoing battle against the cunning Meowfia led by Tawny Catatelli. Are you ready to enforce the law as a dedicated Purrlice officer, or do you prefer to navigate the world as a Meowfia mastermind? Pick your side and embark on an engaging storyline.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mission Meowster</h2>Dive into exciting missions coordinated by fellow feline friends, each one more daring than the last. Prepare yourself for a paw-some journey filled with surprises and challenges!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/cd76e175f0268b305d18cd7ca9a1ac46.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>An open-world sand-box game where you play as a cat, defying the rules and causing mayhem. Climb, scratch, and pounce your way through the cityscape filled with playful challenges and hidden secrets. Customise your cat, team up with friends and let the adventure begin!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/c234a39c3898fe7b7da598219a07d25b.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Cat Chaos</h2>Take your chaos to new heights as you collaborate on the city streets. Hijack cars, cause explosive distractions, and equip a variety of weapons to create the ultimate cat caper. Show off your agile moves with purr-fect parkour skills. Leap from rooftop to rooftop, scale walls, and pull off gravity-defying stunts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/57406107db4d3238e785c35b3c4655d8.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Side</h2>Enter Kitty City, where Chief Hairris’ Purrlice force engages in an ongoing battle against the cunning Meowfia led by Tawny Catatelli. Are you ready to enforce the law as a dedicated Purrlice officer, or do you prefer to navigate the world as a Meowfia mastermind? Pick your side and embark on an engaging storyline.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.poster.avif?t=1729246034\" width=616 height=212 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.webm?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1790360/extras/800888cbaa5f6fbe441e0d7f76e8182b.mp4?t=1729246034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Mission Meowster</h2>Dive into exciting missions coordinated by fellow feline friends, each one more daring than the last. Prepare yourself for a paw-some journey filled with surprises and challenges!",
